3cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11.jpg\" alt=\"Orange accents, custom furniture, and curtainless windows define the interiors of this joyful weekend home. Everything is designed to feel open, natural, and full of life.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-11-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eLocated in the same central space, the dining area continues the home’s relaxed, unpretentious vibe. The family can gather here after a long week in the city, surrounded by trees and light.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12.jpg\" alt=\"Tucked between the home’s modules, the dining area is informal and open. \" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-dining-room-120725-1207-12-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe adjacent kitchen keeps the flow between dining, cooking, and lounging open and social. Materials remain simple and durable, in line with the rest of the home’s palette, clean and industrial, yet full of warmth. The layout prioritizes ease, ideal for weekend cooking with the family.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13.jpg\" alt=\"Minimal and efficient, the open kitchen keeps the layout clean and social. Simple finishes and smart design make it ideal for relaxed family cooking.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-13-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14.jpg\" alt=\"Minimal and efficient, the open kitchen keeps the layout clean and social. Simple finishes and smart design make it ideal for relaxed family cooking.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-kitchen-120725-1207-14-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA relaxed media room that opens fully to the outdoors has a curved sofa, playful green rug, and sculptural lounge chair that adds a casual, creative energy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315.jpg\" alt=\" This cozy media room opens directly to nature. A sculptural sofa and playful green rug add warmth and style to this laid-back escape.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-living-room-120725-1207-1315-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEach bedroom is housed in a separate rectangular module, then visually softened with curved exterior details. This design preserves privacy without closing off the views. Curtainless windows let in the morning light, reinforcing the connection to the outdoors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316.jpg\" alt=\" Private bedroom modules feature curved steel screens for privacy and soft morning light. Curtainless windows offer uninterrupted views of nature.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-bedroom-120725-1207-1316-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317.jpg\" alt=\"A courtyard surrounded by prefabricated modules.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-courtyard-120725-1207-1317-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOutside, a curved swimming pool anchors the landscape. Rodrigo intentionally gave it an unconventional form to echo the organic, playful geometry of the house. It’s sculptural and unexpected, a place for the children to play and the adults to unwind, all surrounded by trees and birdsong.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1279\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318.jpg\" alt=\" A curved pool anchors the garden with its sculptural form. Designed for play and relaxation, it echoes the home’s fluid lines and bold personality.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318-940x626.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/prefab-modular-home-design-swimming-pool-120725-1207-1318-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eRodrigo Ohtake’s Ibiúna retreat is more than just a weekend home, it’s a vision of how modular construction can be joyful, responsive, and deeply rooted in place. Built in just a month but designed with care, this project shows that prefab doesn’t have to mean predictable. It can be expressive, colorful, and in perfect rhythm with the natural world.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by Filippo Bamberghi | Architects: Rodrigo Ohtake Arquitetura e Design | Constuction and Manufacturing: Syshaus\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
